Software Recommendation:		
		
	Software	Comment
UI	Xamarin Studio (Mobile App)	
	Xamarin Android Player (Android emulators)	Available with Free version of the Xamarin
	Kendo UI (Web Page App)	
Server 	C#	
	Web API	
Database	SQL Server	
Report 	Kendo UI	
Project Management	JIRA	
Code Repository	GitHub	
Testing Frameworks	Selenium IDE	Automation testing tool. 
		
		
User Stories:		
As an end user, I want to be able to login via a mobile application and have it remember my credentials.		
As an end user, I want be able to retrieve my forgotten password via email through an option in the mobile application		
As an end user, I want the application to run in the background and be available in the notification drop down list for quick easy access or as a widget I can set on the Home Screen.		
As an end user, I want to be able to enter a new task with a start and finish time against project(s) that I have been assigned to		
As an end user, I want the start time of my new task to be automatically populated with the finish time of my previous task or the current time on my mobile device		
As an end user, I want to be able to lock/submit all the tasks I have entered for the day		
As an end user, I want to be notified if my submitted tasks for the day have been accepted or rejected		
As an end user, I want to be able to modify any tasks that I have entered for the day that have NOT been locked/submitted		
As an end user, I want to be able to see any tasks that I have entered in my calendar on my mobile device		
As an end user, I want to be able to see a summary of the tasks that have been submitted via a report in the app		
As an end user, I want to be able to download the summary as a PDF onto my mobile device or sent via an email		
As an end user, I want to be able to see a graphical representation of the tasks that have been submitted in the app		
As an end user, I want to be able to download the graph as an Excel/PDF onto my mobile device or sent via an email		
As a manager, I want to be able to see a summary of all of the hours spent on specific projects as well as a break down of hours per end user		
As a manager, I want to be able to update the projects that an end user can work on		
As a manager, I want to be notified of all task submissions for the day		
As a manager, I want to be able to Accept any submitted tasks for the day		
As a manager, I want to be able to Reject any submitted tasks for the day and provide a comment as to why it was rejected		
